  - Use dynamic imports for code splitting
  - Implement proper lazy loading for routes
  - Use proper webpack optimization settings
  - Follow the established bundle optimization patterns

  # Component Performance
  - Use v-once for static content that never changes
  - Implement proper component lifecycle management
  - Use computed properties for expensive operations

  # Lazy Loading
  - Use lazy loading for routes with proper loading states
  - Implement proper component lazy loading
  - Use the established lazy loading patterns
  - Follow the established loading state management

  # Rendering Performance
  - Use proper v-if vs v-show patterns
  - Implement proper list rendering with keys
  - Use proper component re-rendering patterns
  - Follow the established rendering optimization patterns

  # Memory Management
  - Use proper component cleanup in beforeDestroy
  - Implement proper event listener cleanup
  - Use proper subscription cleanup
  - Follow the established memory management patterns

  # API Performance
  - Use proper API caching strategies
  - Implement proper request debouncing
  - Use the established API optimization patterns
  - Follow the established request optimization patterns

